{"version":1,"content":"<html>\n<body>\n\n<p>發佈時間：19:33 2026-04-29 HKT</p>\n<img alt=\"「可靠大師」一放到底\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/ur/sthl_square/2b263b37dad1f5692a6f483479796b97/2026-04/r2_11.jpg\"/>\n<p>希斯馬房在第一場憑「滿洛城」贏馬後，在第二場再下一城，上場放到贏馬的「可靠大師」，今晚多負六磅再跑同程，起步後再次採用前領跑法，結果直路上越跑越勁，大勝對手四又四分三馬位而回，潘頓今晚亦有馬贏，希斯令季頭馬數字達至四十八場。</p>\n<p>希斯今晚先在第一場贏「滿洛城」，之後於第二場又為「可靠大師」再下一城，包辦第一口孖寶，令其頭馬數目增至四十八場，在練馬師榜與榜首方嘉柏只差兩場頭馬，冠軍練馬師之爭戰況激烈。</p>\n<p>「可靠大師」馬主施雅治沒有到場，由他的太太Betty和馬販好友派斯拉頭馬。施雅治曾經表示希斯和潘頓都覺得「可靠大師」稚嫩要放頭跑才跑得好，結果馬兒近兩場放頭跑都能取勝，可見騎練的判斷正確。</p>\n<h2>按下圖睇更多相片：</h2>\n<img src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/lr/sthl/c9456b146774843005aa2e7d751f112b/2026-04/3e74b9dc-d7c0-4b79-9a72-6a335fb896a7.jpg\"/>\n<img src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/lr/sthl/cf2d460aa4519f53dbaf79c41e22428b/2026-04/4abf0802-d4b9-48f8-afe1-0877510c6408.jpg\"/>\n<img src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/lr/sthl/a68b4d4b15f0e3f63dfeeb07f8c6bdd1/2026-04/13aa7746-725e-4932-92af-524ab6ea9cb2.jpg\"/>\n<img src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/lr/sthl/1a4691302e6e7c5fd00dfe44fba063a0/2026-04/18f7c255-46b4-4043-adc7-959f1ccbbf18.jpg\"/>\n<img src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/lr/sthl/e5ede4835ebaba6d746cee776ea6ce3b/2026-04/76528cea-1b07-4869-bc8b-fa8f50ae337d.jpg\"/>\n<img src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/lr/sthl/10ef33c7c22140edcce22be88c1e408c/2026-04/aa02f230-819b-4268-ab12-0e8589cea23e.jpg\"/>\n<img src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/lr/sthl/e46c69c90f5ac8dd1b2a2f489f824a9a/2026-04/be6a3d4e-79f4-4ab4-a594-dbab8e93a8ba.jpg\"/>\n<img src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/lr/sthl/ff55a08c3b93b6933dacc922242bbaeb/2026-04/c42d5d63-474f-4687-b025-267504d74a74.jpg\"/>\n<img src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/lr/sthl/cfbd8fae6faee6a44d04610b992e0d17/2026-04/c1638f66-b1e4-432a-b91d-baf7705b7249.jpg\"/>\n<img src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/lr/sthl/29f559a1f2c78d8917d8fd91e5e62ea7/2026-04/cbee9344-e60b-435c-b484-1e267b5a2c4c.jpg\"/>\n<img src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/lr/sthl/ada904210af8beb38aa97298cb40d400/2026-04/cde5708f-5509-4e0d-84d2-850d32b206b0.jpg\"/>\n<img src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/lr/sthl/500d085a74ab603fe7cad5cc23cb4e1c/2026-04/e7d5cd40-d1b3-4ab9-94ba-4317d2743910.jpg\"/>\n</body>\n</html>","scraped_at":"2026-04-29T12:08:17.840347+00:00","quality":{"score":1,"chars":330,"images":13,"source":"星島頭條","fallback":"none"}}